						               													<description>In this game, you try to be the first player to sell all the lemonade at your stand. A deck of numbered &amp;quot;glasses&amp;quot; is dealt evenly to the players. On your turn, you spin the spinner and advance the number of spaces indicated. If you land on a Customer Space, you may place your top glass on it if it is empty, or if the number on your glass is exactly one number above or below the number of the top glass on that space. A Sun Space allows you to place a glass onto any customer space, while a Rain Space just ends your turn. If you land on another player's lemonade stand, you must take a glass from that opponent's pile. If you land on your own lemonade stand, you may give a glass to any player. The first player to run out of glasses is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
